Description: General Purpose Masking Tape is a pressure-sensitive tape designed with a natural rubber adhesive and a crepe paper backing. This design allows for instant stick and reliable holding, making our General Purpose Masking Tape an excellent solution for most general purpose and entry level paint applications.
Features_1: General purpose crepe tape provides solid coverage
Features_2: Ideal for general woodworking, MRO/Construction, paint masking and more
Features_3: Natural rubber adhesive sticks aggressively and holds confidently
Features_4: Crepe paper backing conforms to irregular surfaces and around corners
